                  <name>ibi_done</name>
                  <description>When set to 1, Target Address with Read bit has been transmitted by Target and Controller has either ACKED or NACKed the request for HJ_IBI_RETRY times. If with payload, IBI payload has been transmitted and finished either by End-of-Data (from Target) or STOP (from Controller). Write 1 to clear.</description>
